---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About zzhgod and this blog.">
  <article class="prose-notion">
    <p class="notion-pill w-fit">About</p>
    <h1>About me</h1>
    <p>This is zzhgod's personal blog for AI tools, server operations, research data workflows, and project notes.</p>
    <h2>Focus areas</h2>
    <ul><li>AI tooling and automation workflows</li><li>Docker, Nginx, Cloudflare, and server operations</li><li>Python research data processing and visualization</li><li>Electrochemical impedance and DRT analysis tooling</li></ul>
    <h2>Writing principles</h2>
    <p>Posts should be reproducible, verifiable, and maintainable. The site stays visually close to Notion: quiet, readable, and content-first.</p>
    <h2>Links</h2>
    <p>Follow updates through <a href="https://github.com/zhouzihang0908-wq">GitHub</a> or the RSS feed.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
